<head>
	<title>Glossary of Environmental Terms</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor=#CABB33 link="Maroon" alink="White">


<a href="index.html"><img align=right src="images/small-earth.gif" width=32 height=32 border=0 alt="Return to the UEM Homepage"></a>

